---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Card from '../components/Card.astro';
---

<Layout title="Welcome to Walking On The Edge Studio">
	<main>
		<h1>Walking On The Edge Studio</h1>
		<h2>James Green Fine Art</h2>
		<div class="about">
			<h2>Artist Bio & Statement</h2>
			<p>James is an abstract artist living in the Richmond area. His work is influenced by elements of nature and the outdoors.</p>
			<p>
				His primary mediums are oil with cold wax, acrylics and encaustics. His paintings apply layers of textures to add depth and volume while invoking a visually stimulating and tactile response in the viewer.
			</p>
				
			<p>His approach to painting is very spontaneous and expressive as he endeavors to create a balance between chaos and order.</p>
			
			<p>He is an exhibiting member of the Metropolitan Richmond Artists Association and a member of its board.</p>
		</div>
